<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
From reading what the others have said, these would probably fix wizards (and others)without causing balance problems:<P>Resists on Mobs:  Lower resists on mobs for all casters (duh).  If nothing else, wizards are researchers, planners, studiers, etc.  Therefore, they would realize the value of consistancy and find a way to not be resisted.<P>Cant sit because of agro during:  Make it so that at lvl 45, wizards (or maybe all casters) don't have to sit for meditate to work.  just stand still.<P>Although I'm only lvl 36, I still believe that in the lvls I've been through, the biggest problem has been resists.  It seems that on some nights, I'll have NO resists almost.  Those nights are great.  Some are filled with tons of resists, those, of course, are not so great.  <P><BR>xyle
