<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Absor, <P>You keep making comparisons about rogues being a 3 person damage dealer, etc.  So are we (wizards).  We are interchangable with a rogue's primary function, damage support.<P>Rogues require a tank which require a healer (I will assume you are talking inside a dungeon, and a non-pbae group), so do wizards.  We need a tank to keep the agro, and a healer to heal him, the same as a rogue.<P>As you can see we both have the same role, supplimental damage, we just suck a lot more at doing it.  The problem is, we are not supposed to suck at doing it.  In fact, wizards are supposed to be the BEST at doing it.<P>From experience, wizards are absolutely worthless over time damage-wise without C2 post 50.  Even WITH C2, also from experience, I will say that we do roughly 50% of what damage a melee can do.  Especially if a wizard has C2, that means the melee's have high haste from the chanter.<P>Wizards were supposed to be the most frail but second to none in spell power.  Pre-Kunark, this was the advertisement (Masters of Direct/Arcane Damage), and it was true!  We rocked, people heard the words "Ice Comet", or saw it in action and were in awe.  There was respect toward wizards.<P>This is why you find so many wizards complaining.  This is why you are seeing so many wizards retire.  You have stolen our identity.<P>You have done it, and you do not care.  I know many people, including myself, have sent you TONS of ideas that will work, regardless what "definitely nots" you have laid down.  We have done this for a LONG time now Absor, and nothing, absolutely NOTHING has been done to redeem our class.<P>Even if you DON'T care Absor, WE DO!  How many hours do you think many of us have in our characters?  You think that is just easy to throw away?  Even if you don't care Absor, it is your job to hear our concerns, and if they are valid, make sure they are fixed.  You have already admitted they are valid, now quit stalling and tell them to fix our class!<P>Rondeveron Stormsmith (52 wizard -Retired-)<BR>Lifty Swiftpocket (54 rogue)<P>--------------------<P>Lifty Swiftpocket (Rake)<BR>Rondeveron Stormsmith (Channeler)<BR>of Karana
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="1"  face="Verdana, Arial">
 Posts: <B>3</B>  &nbsp;|&nbsp; IP: <A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/eq/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=get_ip&f=3&t=002458&reply_num=000150">Logged</A>
</FONT>
</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>


</table></td></tr></table>
</center>


